# NICOLE JENNY MOD MINECRAFT

NICOLE JENNY MOD delivers immersive companion gameplay for Minecraft through advanced NPC entity creation and interactive AI technology. Based on the popular Jenny mod concept, this standalone modification introduces lifelike human NPCs with customizable appearances, interactive behaviors, and relationship systems that respond to player actions.

