## Installation Steps

1. Download the .rar archive using the link above
2. Extract contents using WinRAR or 7-Zip
3. Ensure Minecraft Forge is installed (1.12.2, 1.16.5, or 1.18.2)
4. Copy the .jar file into your Minecraft mods folder
5. Launch Minecraft with the Forge profile
6. Find spawn egg in creative inventory or craft using mod recipe

---

## Features

• Fully Interactive NPCs – create custom human companions with unique appearances and personalities
• Advanced AI System – NPCs follow, perform tasks, and react to environment with realistic pathfinding
• Relationship Mechanics – build affinity through gifts and conversation; unlocks special interactions
• Customization Options – modify skin, hair, clothing, and accessories using in-game menus
• Dialogue Interface – conversation trees with multiple response options
• Task Assignment – assign NPCs to farm, mine, or collect items
• Multiplayer Support – NPCs sync across connected players

